28:17.196 --> 28:19.999
a trans activist
for the last 40 years.

28:20.032 --> 28:21.801
GRACY: We're here.
And we're not going nowhere.

28:21.834 --> 28:24.937
I am not going down
without a goddamn fight.

28:24.971 --> 28:26.806
