Get us that card, baby.

58:37.281 --> 58:39.784
O70, zero.
Bingo!

58:39.817 --> 58:42.753
Aww.

58:45.022 --> 58:47.592
Where'd you grow up?
Indiana originally.

58:47.625 --> 58:49.193
That's where I'm from.
Yeah.

58:49.226 --> 58:51.796
So what was it like growing up
in Indiana when you were young?

58:51.829 --> 58:53.297
Well, I was bullied

58:53.330 --> 58:56.166
after they found out
that I was a homosexual.

58:56.200 --> 58:57.334
Yeah.
There was no such word

58:57.367 --> 58:58.903
as gay.
Right.

58:58.936 --> 59:01.105
And then I went to transform,

59:01.138 --> 59:03.073
to become a woman.

59:03.107 --> 59:06.143
And I got dra--
involved with drugs

59:06.176 --> 59:07.612
and everything.
Mm.

59:07.645 --> 59:09.079
You know,
and then getting in pro--

59:09.113 --> 59:12.249
to prostitution and going
to jail so many times.

59:12.282 --> 59:14.184
And then, one day,
I just finally decided

59:14.218 --> 59:15.820
I can't take it anymore
and left.

59:15.853 --> 59:20.124
But I overcome that
after I joined the Army.

59:20.157 --> 59:21.792
Ah.
Which I kept it secret,

59:21.826 --> 59:24.094
you know, that --
that I was who I was.

59:24.128 --> 59:26.363
And so to be here, it just means
that you can live freely.

59:26.396 --> 59:29.800
I can be myself. And where I was
at before, for 30 years,

59:29.834 --> 59:32.302
I was scared to walk
down the hall to go outside.

59:32.336 --> 59:33.871
This is my home, you know?

59:33.904 --> 59:36.306
And I love everybody here.

59:36.340 --> 59:38.743
And where are you from?
I was born in L.A.,

59:38.776 --> 59:42.379
and back then,
it was very difficult.

59:42.412 --> 59:45.816
I struggled as a kid
with mom and dad

59:45.850 --> 59:48.052
coming from Orthodox Jews.

59:48.085 --> 59:51.088
But God loves us just the way
that we are.

59:51.121 --> 59:54.124
It doesn't matter
how anybody else thinks.

59:54.158 --> 59:55.793
It's okay to be who you are.

59:55.826 --> 59:58.863
I was in a relationship
for 36 years.

59:58.896 --> 1:00:02.032
We raised a son together,
so my son had two mommies.

1:00:02.066 --> 1:00:03.267
Awesome.

1:00:03.300 --> 1:00:05.803
And my other half passed away,

1:00:05.836 --> 1:00:08.906
and then I met Nancy.

1:00:08.939 --> 1:00:10.875
Oh, you guys are a couple?

1:00:10.908 --> 1:00:12.643
Yes.
Ah!

1:00:12.677 --> 1:00:15.279
She's just been more
than a friend to me.

1:00:15.312 --> 1:00:18.849
I mean, she's just been there,
you know, to pick up the pieces.

1:00:18.883 --> 1:00:22.720
And, uh, and this place
is such a safe haven

1:00:22.753 --> 1:00:25.089
because if you live
anywhere else,

1:00:25.122 --> 1:00:28.693
you have to pretend
to be somebody else.

1:00:28.726 --> 1:00:31.929
**

1:00:31.962 --> 1:00:33.330
PAGE:
It wasn't so long ago that

1:00:33.363 --> 1:00:35.199
to live openly
as a gay

1:00:35.232 --> 1:00:38.903
or trans American
would be unimaginable.

1:00:38.936 --> 1:00:40.370
Even though many
of their partners

1:00:40.404 --> 1:00:42.406
were unable to see this day,

1:00:42.439 --> 1:00:45.142
our queer elders
have seen enormous change

1:00:45.175 --> 1:00:47.044
right before their eyes.

1:00:47.077 --> 1:00:49.113
They've come
from being considered criminals

1:00:49.146 --> 1:00:50.347
under the law,

1:00:50.380 --> 1:00:52.216
to seeing their love celebrated

1:00:52.249 --> 1:00:54.719
by the highest court
in the land.

1:00:54.752 --> 1:00:56.453
Where would I be
without the passion

1:00:56.486 --> 1:00:58.789
and determination
of the generations

1:00:58.823 --> 1:01:00.858
that came before me?

1:01:00.891 --> 1:01:02.092
Dennis, help me.

1:01:02.126 --> 1:01:03.460
Woo-hoo!

1:01:07.064 --> 1:01:10.868
PAGE: Ian and I have come
to the end of our journey,

1:01:10.901 --> 1:01:13.904
but part of my motivation
in doing this series was to work

1:01:13.938 --> 1:01:15.806
through my own thoughts
and feelings

1:01:15.840 --> 1:01:18.843
about what it means
to be gay in America.

1:01:18.876 --> 1:01:20.845
Growing up, for me,

1:01:20.878 --> 1:01:22.980
I started acting
at a very young age,

1:01:23.013 --> 1:01:26.383
and then, bam, I went from being
an anonymous person,

1:01:26.416 --> 1:01:27.952
to not an anonymous person.

1:01:27.985 --> 1:01:29.854
And that's when it felt like,

1:01:29.887 --> 1:01:31.889
"Hey, nobody can know
you were gay."

1:01:31.922 --> 1:01:34.258
It's not a nice way to live.

