1:01:37.762 --> 1:01:38.896
So pretty.
Oh, thanks.

1:01:38.929 --> 1:01:40.097
And your shoes?

1:01:40.130 --> 1:01:42.867
Um, I don't know.

1:01:42.900 --> 1:01:44.334
Oh, you got to rehearse
this stuff.

1:01:44.368 --> 1:01:48.272
I'm just, you know,
I'm horrible.

1:01:48.305 --> 1:01:50.741
And I feel like we met in a time
where we were both feeling

1:01:50.775 --> 1:01:53.510
that exploring about
how to get through that

1:01:53.543 --> 1:01:55.946
and how we bonded.

1:01:55.980 --> 1:01:57.347
We were both going
through something similar.

1:01:57.381 --> 1:01:59.283
It's like we're
both figuring out how to --

1:01:59.316 --> 1:02:01.518
how to navigate our various,
different worlds

1:02:01.551 --> 1:02:03.788
with our sexuality in mind.

1:02:03.821 --> 1:02:06.957
Ellen is my family,
and she's the friend

1:02:06.991 --> 1:02:09.359
that I have that I can
talk about issues with.

1:02:09.393 --> 1:02:11.428
You know, Ian will be my --
my family for life,

1:02:11.461 --> 1:02:12.930
no doubt on my mind.
Mm-hmm.

1:02:12.963 --> 1:02:14.765
You know?
And a big part of that, I think,

1:02:14.799 --> 1:02:18.268
is getting to find a friend who,

1:02:18.302 --> 1:02:19.904
together, you work through that.

1:02:19.937 --> 1:02:22.973
That's some very, very,
very special thing.

1:02:23.007 --> 1:02:25.042
Loving other people starts
with loving ourselves

1:02:25.075 --> 1:02:27.912
